Clean. The positioning now uses CSS classes:

panel-right: left = anchor (card right edge), panel extends rightward naturally
panel-left: left = anchor (card left edge), transform: translateX(-100%) pulls the panel fully leftward, keeping the panel flush against the card with no gap
The sub-panel follows the same logic relative to the main panel — it opens right if there's room, otherwise flips left using the same transform trick.



